				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I personally thing TLC is a pretty petty plan.  The way I got it figured is that high lvl players have just as much right to go after an item as a low lvl person, and this is coming from someone whos highest char is only 20.  Especially in a new area that the higher levels hadnt had a chance to receive the items in when they were younger since the zone wasnt there.  I have never had a problem with higher end people camping stuff I wanted to camp most of the time if they are there they will help me and move over and let me camp.  Maybe I am just lucky to be on a good server I dont know but that is my experience in it.  Well that is my 2cp not really flaming the TLC I just think that the people that are for it are just not thinking it all the way through like the guy below me says the lowbies pay their 10 dollars a month just like high levels well there are two ways to look at that.  <BR>
Weslyn Bigfeet<BR>
